msgctxt "#31268"
msgid "You have to restart Kodi for this option to take effect once the option has been activated. TMDb and Trakt should work out of the box. Metacritic and Rottentomatoes ratings require an OMDb API key. Get an OMDb API Key at http://www.omdbapi.com/apikey.aspx and afterward input the OMDb API Key into the TheMovieDb Helper settings."
msgstr "Morate ponovo pokrenuti Kodi kako bi ova opcija stupila na snagu nakon što je opcija aktivirana.TMDb i Trakt bi trebali raditi odmah.Metacritic i Rottentomatos ocjene zahtijevaju OMDb API ključ.Nabavite OMDb API ključ na http://www.omdbapi.com/apikey.aspx i nakon toga unesite OMDb API ključ u postavke TheMovieDb Helper."

