msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Hvala što koristite Aeon Tajo—stvarno se nadam da uživate.Stvaranje i održavanje ovakvog Kodi skina zahtijeva stotine sati rada.Ako je Aeon Tajo nešto u čemu uživate i smatrate korisnim, njegova podrška mi pomaže da nastavim raditi na njemu i osigurava da se može nastaviti razvijati u budućnosti.[CR][CR]Ako se tako odlučite, primat ćete česta ažuriranja s novim značajkama i ispravcima grešaka, zajedno s videozapisima, medijskim paketima i člancima koje je lako pratiti s detaljnim savjetima koji će vam pomoći da izvučete najviše iz svega što Aeon Tajo nudi, zajedno s mojom iskrenom zahvalnošću za vašu podršku.[CR][CR]Za više informacija posjetite [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] i potražite kreatora [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR] ili idite na [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Hvala!"

